		accountId
		token
		name

		expiresAt
		createdAt
		updatedAt
	}
}

query ($id:ID)

	oAuthFindAccessTokenById (id:$id)
	{

		name
		isRevoked
		expiresAt
		createdAt
		updatedAt
	}
}

mutation ($payload:OAuthUpdateAccessTokenInput!)

	{

		accountId
		token
		name
		isRevoked
		expiresAt
		createdAt
		updatedAt
	}
}

mutation ($id:ID!)

		name
		isRevoked
		expiresAt
		createdAt
		updatedAt
	}
}

mutation ($query:QueryStatement)

		expiresAt

	}
}
